channel.title: My first source - Hollowfied Dreams
channel.description:
Well it isn't anything special.. But I think it passes to be my first source released.
Source I used: Dannyscape V2
What I have added -
- Other from godsword stances that were already added I added:
- Defender emote,.
- Crossbow emote.
- Veng other emote and GFX.
- A 95% teleother spell working in mage book.
- A new home.
- Draconic visage (working when used on a anti dragon shield.
- All sigils (all working when used on a blessed spirit shield).
- Added 474 whip attack emote and 500 stand emote.
- A auto trimming skillcape system.
- I also added the extra 3 Godwars bosses Sara is NOT animated, K'rill Tsutaroth, Kree 'Arra are only have animated I could not get there blocking and attacking working.
- I've added many new Runescape items, such as: Flared Trousers, God cloaks, Ardougne Cloak 3, New fury look, Rocktail with healing and Cavefish with healing, Dragon Pickaxe, Dragon Gaunts. (there's much more that you can see for yourself, I only have 2 non Runescape items in the game.)
Client and Source are in a package: http://uppit.com/uz8huxvdlpjp/Hollowfied_Dreams.rar
Pictures:
[IMG]http://i764.photobucket.com/albums/xx290/yobert30/untitled-6-1.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i764.photobucket.com/albums/xx290/yobert30/gsstuff-1.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i764.photobucket.com/albums/xx290/yobert30/Gsspec-1.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i764.photobucket.com/albums/xx290/yobert30/Defendemote-1.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i764.photobucket.com/albums/xx290/yobert30/cbow-1.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i764.photobucket.com/albums/xx290/yobert30/whip-1.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i764.photobucket.com/albums/xx290/yobert30/untitled3-1.jpg[/img]
Customs there are above: New fury look from Runescape, The new fishes: Rocktail and Cavefish, Ardougne Cloak 3 from Runescape, Chaotic Maul, Raw Rocktail (is cookable), Draconic Visage, Dragon Pickaxe (is able to mine with), The new look for herbs, All the sigils for spirit shields, All the god cloaks, Dragon Boots, Dragon Claws.
[IMG]http://i764.photobucket.com/albums/xx290/yobert30/untitled4-1.jpg[/img]
[size=12pt]ALL OF THE ABOVE WERE CODED BY ME EXCEPT FOR THE GODSWORD STANCES AND SPECIAL ATTACKING[/size]
- That's all I can do at the moment please enjoy my first release.
Credits too: Danny
Jagex
Me (Hollowfied)
